parameters.name: Ipv4Prefix
parameters.description: IPv4 prefix N. Valid values of N: 1 to 10.

parameters.name: PrivateIpAddress
parameters.description: Secondary private IP address N to unassign. Valid values of N: 1 to 32.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The region ID of the ENI. You can call the [DescribeRegions](~~25609~~) operation to query the most recent region list.
